HEADWORD: Gemsbok
<hw>Gems"bok</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[D.; akin to G.
<ets>gemsbock</ets> the male or buck of the chamois; <ets>gemse</ets>
chamois, goat of the Alps + <ets>bock</ets> buck.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A South African antelope (<spn>Oryx
Capensis</spn>), having long, sharp, nearly straight horns.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

